1,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d48ebebe880d8baddb28f9a0e4342f5877512351","tid":1101223,"uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtHUS40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtHUS40.jpg&h=c326bf79&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"去到邊都捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c617f7e55c15d50bc47ff758dd921fc1ecad4e5e","tid":1101223,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:51:03.000Z","msg":"慘啦， 剩底時間陪下老豆老母。"},{"pid":"c1e27afb994d12ec20f60c0123d6f3db23ebca95","tid":1101223,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc14a2eb2b43762c5310e7621424d5e14b8f8c4c","tid":1101223,"uid":49316,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9391c873808dd437704bfdb74d2fb4baa1144ebf","tid":1101223,"uid":195264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"057dbf2dcf2151a3de168c6370438fb59ca19c60","tid":1101223,"uid":65686,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"喺知乎睇到嘅一個人嘅評論：<br />\n<br />\n在英國讀書的時候偶然遇到一個香港來的中年人，他是12年才移民到英國的。九七大限之前，他的家人都移民海外，他當時很愛國，死都不肯跟家人一起走，他妻子帶著孩子移民英國，他獨自留在香港。（這愛國愛到妻兒都不要了，跟毛時代的紅衛兵有得一拼。後來他熱衷於參加社會活動，遊行支持民建聯什麼的，一切看來很理想，直到10年。他那年拿特區護照到南美旅行被一個旅店老闆誤認為是小偷，後來警察來抓他，他好不容易拿著護照跑到中國大使館，被拒絕入內，說香港護照不受理，去自首雲雲。他當時想死的心都有了，這時他聽到了一個人講英語，想到了自己還有一本bno，但拿到特區護照後根本沒用過，不知道扔哪裡了。他抱著最後一絲希望跑到英國領事館，工作人員得知他是海外國民就讓他進去了。他謊稱bno丟了，但人家還是查到他的信息說他已經十年沒有續領bno了，他聽了一陣尷尬，生怕英國使館也不管他了。但工作人員又說英國海外國民身份終身有效，所以讓他在使館招待所住下，又派人去核實情況，這件事搞了十多天，他終於清白了，就當即補領了身份證明，出門就撕了特區護照。後來回到香港，以親人團聚為名申請移民英國，一年後獲批。我當時聽了一陣心酸。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"呢段要copy低。長期回覆五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他當時想死的心都有了</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e42e8a2f969866d06353fd89f5909948826e5ce","tid":1101223,"uid":77092,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}